title: Southern Lehigh's Nina DeLuna is lehighvalleylive Girls Tennis Player of the Week
text:
Nina DeLuna , Southern Lehigh 
DeLuna won the Colonial League No. 1 singles tournament on Monday with an 8-1 win over Palisades' Madeline Newsome in the final. 
The junior will go for District 11 Class AAA gold on Monday when she plays Easton's Elessa Jacobs in the tournament final. 
She has lost only two games in her four matches in the district tournament. 
HONORABLE MENTION: Fr. Elessa Jacobs , Easton; So. Tyra Ott , Wilson; Fr. Natalie Sinai , Freedom; Sr. Madelyn Conrad , Liberty; Fr. Logan Lencheski , Notre Dame; Fr. Brenna Magliochetti , Bethlehem Catholic; Sr. Katie Cole , Southern Lehigh; Jr. Julia Mowrey , Notre Dame; Danielle Barnes , Southern Lehigh; Lucy Zhang , Southern Lehigh; Kelly Asselin , Southern Lehigh; Keelin McLoughlin , Southern Lehigh.
